# Mereka Backend v2 - Node.js Migration

🎉 **Production-Quality Backend Setup Complete!**

Production-grade Node.js backend for migrating Mereka from Firebase to MongoDB with **professional quality standards**.

---

## 📦 What's Included

✅ **Fastify 5.x** - High-performance web framework
✅ **MongoDB + Mongoose** - Flexible document database
✅ **TypeScript 5.9 (Strict)** - Professional strict type safety
✅ **Biome** - Unified linting and formatting
✅ **Swagger/OpenAPI** - Auto-generated API docs
✅ **Vitest** - Fast testing (80%+ coverage target)
✅ **JWT Authentication** - Secure auth ready
✅ **Validation Scripts** - Professional quality gates
✅ **AI Agent Workflows** - 8 specialized agents
✅ **Example User Module** - Complete reference implementation

---

## 🚀 Quick Start (3 Commands)

```bash
npm install              # Install dependencies
cp .env.example .env     # Configure (edit with MongoDB URI)
npm run dev              # Start server
```

**Visit**: http://localhost:3000/docs (Swagger documentation)

See **[QUICK-START.md](./QUICK-START.md)** for detailed setup.

